SUMMARY:Art Battle Lancaster - March Event
DESCRIPTION:Art Battle Lancaster is a live\, high-energy painting competition where artists create original works in front of an audience. During each round\, selected artists have just 20 minutes to transform a blank canvas into a finished painting while guests watch the creative process unfold in real time. \n\n\n\nAt the end of each round\, the audience votes for their favorite artist to advance to the final round\, where the night’s champion is crowned. The fast-paced format makes every round exciting\, as creativity\, speed\, and style all play a role in winning over the crowd. \n\n\n\nAll of the paintings created during the competition will be available in a silent auction\, giving attendees the opportunity to take home one-of-a-kind artwork created during the event. \n\n\n\nIn addition to the tournament rounds\, the evening will feature a special guest artist painting live throughout the event. That finished piece will also be auctioned at the end of the night. \n\n\n\nArt Battle Lancaster brings together artists\, art lovers\, and the local community for a fun and energetic night celebrating creativity. Whether you are cheering on your favorite painter\, discovering new artists\, or hoping to take home a piece of original artwork\, every Art Battle event offers a unique experience.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/art-battle-lancaster-march-event/
LOCATION:West Art Community Center\, 816 Buchanan Ave\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Arts and Culture
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/AB3095-Lancaster-19MAR26A5-Large.jpeg
ORGANIZER;CN="Art Battle Lancaster":MAILTO:artbattlelancaster@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
