DESCRIPTION:Casual Comedy Camaraderie Their Royal Laziness is one of LIP’s longest running teams of improvisers! Their shows are entertaining and unpredictable\, as they bring a playful and relaxed energy to the stage. Expect the unexpected from these maginificent majesties! BYOB $15 at the door Due to the size of our theater\, there is a quick turnover time between our scheduled shows. If you purchase tickets to both events on Friday evening\, you will be asked to wait outside during the break so that the next team can warm up before the audience returns. LANCASTER IMPROV PLAYERS is an intimate black box venue located in the heart of Lancaster City. With a capacity of approximately 30 guests\, that means this Lancaster comedy club is entirely front row. Not a nosebleed in sight! After all\, BYOB is just a drink special you never get tired of.
