DESCRIPTION:Lancaster’s Monthly Improv Game Show Hosted By Austin Rittle From the whacky mind of Austin Rittle comes Lancaster’s own game show! Join us every month for a hilarious competition of comedians making it all up as they go. Each season has it’s own cast of contestants that get pulled from\, so come cheer your friends on! BYOB $15 at the door Due to the size of our theater\, there is a quick turnover time between our scheduled shows. If you purchase tickets to both events on Saturday evening\, you will be asked to wait outside during the break so that the next team can warm up before the audience returns. LANCASTER IMPROV PLAYERS is an intimate black box venue located in the heart of Lancaster City. With a capacity of approximately 30 guests\, that means this Lancaster comedy club is entirely front row. Not a nosebleed in sight! After all\, BYOB is just a drink special you never get tired of.
