SUMMARY:Spring Fling: A Day with Schiffer Craft Publishing at Gallery Grow
DESCRIPTION:Schiffer Craft Spring Pop-Up! 20% off kits\, try-before-you-buy crochet + watercolor table\, and a fun yarn guess giveaway. \n\n\n\nJoin us at Gallery Grow for a special Schiffer Craft pop-up filled with hands-on creativity.The Schiffer Craft team will be on site hosting a crochet and watercolor paint-along as part of a “try before you buy” experience. Pull up a chair at the activity table\, test out the kits\, ask questions\, and see what sparks before taking one home. \n\n\n\nAll Schiffer Craft kits will be 20% off during the event. \n\n\n\nWe’ll also have a Guess the Yarn Length jar — the closest guess wins a free Peapod Kit (entries include email sign-ups for both Schiffer Craft and Gallery Grow). The first 25 customers who make a purchase will receive a free Schiffer Craft tote. \n\n\n\nThese kits make thoughtful\, creative additions to Easter baskets — perfect for teens\, adults\, and anyone who’d love an experience instead of more candy. Come play\, get inspired\, and discover your next creative obsession. \n\n\n\nhttp://www.schiffercraft.com/
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/spring-fling-a-day-with-schiffer-craft-publishing-at-gallery-grow/
LOCATION:Gallery Grow Plant Bar\, 320 N Queen St.\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes and Workshops,Free Events and Activites
