SUMMARY:Spring EggStravaganza
DESCRIPTION:A beloved Tiny Town tradition where families come together to celebrate Spring and Easter!Hop on down to Tiny Town for an all-inclusive Easter experience designed with toddlers in mind. Enjoy relaxed play\, sweet spring activities\, and thoughtful moments that let families slow down and truly enjoy the day together. \n\n\n\nWhat’s IncludedRelaxed\, controlled\, kid-friendly Easter Egg Hunt in our playhousesEaster egg decorating stationCanvas tote included for every childUnlimited photos with the Easter BunnyUnlimited Duck Donuts and fresh fruitGoat snuggling stationPlay in all 12 luxury playhousesAnd as always\, our epic bubble dance partyTiny Town Easter eventEaster Egg Hunt at Tiny Town \n\n\n\nSpring fun at Tiny TownWhy do we sell this event out every year? Families love the value\, the calm experience\, and the way this event is thoughtfully planned\, which is why they come back year after year. \n\n\n\nNo mad dashes or tears here. Our Easter Egg Hunt is intentionally slow-paced and gentle\, giving every child time to participate without crowds or chaos. \n\n\n\nEvent DetailsSunday\, March 29\, 202610:00am to 12:00pm1:00pm to 3:00pm4:00pm to 6:00pm
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/spring-eggstravaganza/
LOCATION:Tiny Town\, 533 Janet Ave.\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17601\, United States
CATEGORIES:Family Fun,Holiday,Special Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/Vzzs-Large.jpeg
