SUMMARY:Gallery Grow 1 Year on Queen Street Celebration
DESCRIPTION:Gallery Grow Plant Bar is celebrating our ONE YEAR since opening on Queen Street and you’re invited! Join us on Friday\, April 3rd and Saturday\, April 4th to enjoy 20% off Plants and Pottery. Plus\, take part in a Golden Egg Anniversary Hunt – with prizes inside! No purchase necessary.  \n\n\n\nOn Friday\, April 3rd\, we’re keeping the celebration going for First Friday\, with extended hours until 8PM\, featuring artwork by Laura Alvis\, live music\, and complimentary sangria while you shop or create a project!  \n\n\n\nCome celebrate a year of plants\, creativity\, and community with us on Queen Street!
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/gallery-grow-1-year-on-queen-street-celebration/
LOCATION:Gallery Grow Plant Bar\, 320 N Queen St.\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Family Fun,First Friday,Free Events and Activites
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/GG-1-year-on-Queen-Celebration-header-384-x-480-px.jpeg
ORGANIZER;CN="Gallery Grow Plant Bar":MAILTO:contact@gallerygrow.com
END:VEVENT
