SUMMARY:Saturday Night Improv: Peach Soda
DESCRIPTION:Crack open an ice cold can of charismatic comedy! \n\n\n\nHilarious games and silly scenes abound in this monthly improv showcase from Lancaster Improv Players’ legendary house team PEACH SODA. Watch as this team of expert players deftly transforms your suggestions into a refreshing array of punchlines & parables – then after the show\, try improv for yourself at the free PEACH JAM! \n\n\n\nBYOB \n\n\n\n$15 at the door \n\n\n\nThe improv jam typically begins around 10:00pm. \n\n\n\nDue to the size of our theater\, there is a quick turnover time between our scheduled shows. If you purchase tickets to both events on Saturday evening\, you will be asked to wait outside during the break so that the next team can warm up before the audience returns. \n\n\n\nABOUT PEACH SODA \n\n\n\nPeach Soda combines short form improv games and long form improv scenes that keep you on the edge of your seat! To ensure every performance is one of a kind\, the focus of the team shifts every few months to learn new skills so the flavor is always fresh. They even recently added new team members! Peach Soda performs the first Saturday of every month at 8:30pm in the Lancaster Improv Players theater and is coached by Angie Springer. \n\n\n\nLANCASTER IMPROV PLAYERS is an intimate black box venue located in the heart of Lancaster City. With a capacity of approximately 30 guests\, that means this Lancaster comedy club is entirely front row. Not a nosebleed in sight! After all\, BYOB is just a drink special you never get tired of.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/saturday-night-improv-peach-soda-3/
LOCATION:Lancaster Improv Players\, 16 S Prince St\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Theatre
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/Peach-Soda-2.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Lancaster Improv Players":MAILTO:kate@lancasterimprovplayers.org
END:VEVENT
