SUMMARY:LANCASTER COUNTY’S BEST KEPT SECRETS TOUR
DESCRIPTION:LANCASTER COUNTY’S BEST KEPT SECRETS TOUR— April 9 thru 25\, 2026 A shopping/food and fun adventure featuring 44 off-the-beaten path businesses. Set up like a home or garden tour\, you’ll travel place to place enjoying all the special free things (refreshments\, games\, gifts\, demos\, etc) the businesses have planned for you. Plus\, each place has given you a valuable coupon. What a fun way to explore Lancaster County! Tickets are $12ea–$1 per ticket is donated to Lancaster Snow Angels. Call 717-721-9409 or email: melissa@bestkeptsecretstour.com #bestkeptsecretstour #lancastercounty #smallbusinessshopping #shopsmall #freestuff #discounts #ticketsavailable #explore #daytrip #bkst
